text: Happy New Year! :tada: :tada: :tada: Starting a late night quiet stream! We will be doing some studying, tweaking some learning tools that I wrote in Julia, and examining Franklin.jl! My goal is to get the new So Simple theme for Franklin with <@UDP5WL2RX> ready for you all soon! Feel free to join in, chill out to some low-key music, and say hello! <https://www.twitch.tv/thecedarprince>

attachments.text: My name is Jacob Zelko! My background is in biomedical engineering, biomedical informatics, and healthcare. I enjoy programming in Julia and Python. I find it even more fun with others! Welcome to the stream one and all!
